meta.job_title: Travel Nurse RN Labor and Delivery

duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide nursing care for expectant mothers in labor, delivery, and postpartum period.
Monitor maternal and fetal well-being and provide support and education to new mothers.
Collaborate with physicians and other healthcare professionals to ensure comprehensive care for patients.
Adhere to hospital policies and procedures, maintain accurate patient records, and ensure a safe and clean environment.

education_certification.credential: BLS, ACLS, NRP, and Stable certifications required
Active Texas or compact RN license required
2 or more years of recent labor and delivery experience
